WEBVTT

00:01.260 --> 00:01.860
15.

00:16.260 --> 00:22.100
And I saw another sign in heaven, great and marvellous, seven angels having the seven

00:22.100 --> 00:26.160
last plagues, for in them is filled up the wrath of God.

00:26.700 --> 00:32.980
And I saw, as it were, a sea of glass mingled with fire, and them that had gotten the victory

00:32.980 --> 00:37.880
over the beast, and over his image, and over his mark, and over the number of his name,

00:38.400 --> 00:41.720
stand on the sea of glass, having the harps of God.

00:41.920 --> 00:47.240
And they sing the song of Moses, the servant of God, and the song of the Lamb, saying,

00:47.240 --> 00:53.140
Great and marvellous are thy works, Lord God Almighty!

00:53.880 --> 00:57.380
Just and true are thy ways, thou King of saints!

00:57.940 --> 01:01.860
Who shall not fear thee, O Lord, and glorify thy name?

01:02.180 --> 01:08.500
For thou only art holy, for all nations shall come and worship before thee, for thy judgments

01:08.500 --> 01:10.320
are made manifest.

01:10.880 --> 01:17.140
And after that I looked, and behold, the temple of the tabernacle of the testimony in heaven

01:17.140 --> 01:23.140
was opened, and the seven angels came out of the temple, having the seven plagues, clothed

01:23.140 --> 01:27.580
in pure and white linen, and having their breasts girded with golden girdles.

01:27.920 --> 01:34.420
And one of the four beasts gave unto the seven angels seven golden vials, full of the wrath

01:34.420 --> 01:37.120
of God, who liveth for ever and ever.

01:37.520 --> 01:43.100
And the temple was filled with smoke from the glory of God and from his power, and no

01:43.100 --> 01:48.880
was able to enter into the temple till the seven plagues of the seven angels were fulfilled.

01:50.320 --> 01:52.220
The end of chapter 15.

